    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA184-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">ET: 1. itu makaṭ pōkkiya tāy teruṭṭum ayalil āṭṭiyarkku uraittatu.
            2. maṉaimaruṭci.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">ET: 1. This is what the mother who had let [her] daughter go said to the neighbour women who imforned [her]. 2. Refusal of the house.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA184">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            orumaka ḷuṭaiyēṉ maṉṉē yavaḷuñ</l>
<l>            cerumiku moympiṟ kūrvēṟ kāḷaiyoṭu</l>
<l>            perumalai yaruñcura nerunaṟ ceṉṟaṉa</l>
<l>            ḷiṉiyē</l>
<l>            tāṅkuniṉ ṉavala meṉṟi ratumaṟ</l>
<l>            ṟiyāṅkaṉa mollumō vaṟivuṭai yīrē </l>
<l>            yuḷḷi ṉuḷḷam vēmē yuṇkaṇ</l>
<l>            maṇivāḻ pāvai naṭaikaṟ ṟaṉṉave</l>
<l>            ṉaṇiyiyaṟ kuṟumaka ḷāṭiya</l>
<l>            maṇiyēr nocciyun teṟṟiyuṅ kaṇṭē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>I had one daughter, for sure.</l>
<l rend="indent4">And she</l>
<l>has gone yesterday to the difficult desert of big mountains</l>
<l rend="indent">with a young man with a sharp spear, very valorous in fight.</l>
<l>Now,</l>
<l>endure your affliction, you may say.</l>
<l rend="indent4">That of all things,</l>
<l>how is it possible [to us], o you who possess knowledge?</l>
<l>When I remember [my] inside burns</l>
<l rend="indent2">– seeing the sapphire-like Nocci tree and the verandah</l>
<l rend="indent2">where my decorated little daughter played,</l>
<l rend="indent3">as if [my] pupil, the sapphire living in [my] kajal eye,</l>
<l rend="indent4">had learned to walk.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
